				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">make mages THE pet class again. They don't want to give us any defensive spells because it goes against some yet to be defined <span style="font-style: italic">class definition</span>. Then give me a REAL PET.
<br />

<br />
I would GLADLY trade in ALL my nukes for <a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=14639" target="_blank" class="postlink">a mountain pooka</a>
<br />

<br />
The amount of damage these creatures do is INSANE.  Who needs nukes when you have a pooka? I won't need any defensive spells with a pooka.
<br />

<br />
Got Pooka?
<br />

<br />
Seriously, I know the inherent risks with pooka charming. Charm broke on the pooka and killed the chanter which then ripped through the rest of our group in about 1min or less. This kind of power is awesome, but its incredible to see what a hasted, armed, fero'd pooka can do.
<br />

<br />

<br />
take half our nukes and give us mini-Pooka?<br />_________________<br /><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=157603>Arch Mage Rotlom Xavier</a>
