Please do tell what use you have found for the 51+fire pet?  I'm still trying to figure out a meaningful use for him.
<br />

<br />
I made this post to illustrate the SERIOUS damage that a charmed pooka can do. People have parsed them at over 1800DPS. That is an insanely powerful tool.  Anyone that hasn't seen it first hand cannot appreciate how quickly they can drop mobs. 
<br />

<br />
Having something even marginally comparable to that would be a boon to mages everywhere. We lack the power we once had. No one can deny that.  The fact that our epic pet was still the BEST pet for so very long tells how far the class has fallen behind in relative power. Since they don't want to restore that power, we need defensive spells. 
<br />

<br />
END OF STORY.<br />_________________<br /><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=157603>Arch Mage Rotlom Xavier</a>
<br />
69 Human Arch Convoker of Mithaniel Marr
